snippet.title: Deep Rock Galactic Season 2: Rival Escalation Official Steam Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Subscribe now! https://bit.ly/2CVu6yi

Today, Ghost Ship Games and Coffee Stain Publishing have launched Deep Rock Galactic’s highly anticipated Season 02: Rival Escalation update on Steam and will launch on Xbox and PlayStation on May 5th, 2022.
